content: It is impossible to say who would win a fight between One Punch Man and Goku as it depends on the specific circumstances of the fight and the versions of the characters being used. In the manga and anime version of One Punch Man, Saitama is depicted as having the ability to defeat any opponent with just one punch, but it is not clear if he can defeat an opponent as powerful as Goku. In the Dragon Ball series, Goku has several powerful abilities and transformations that give him an edge in battle. It would be a close fight, but it is hard to say who would come out victorious.
